Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.42,0:03:18.38,title-03,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,440)\bord1\3c&H99A434&\blur1\pos(860,610)}#07  高明的約會邀請技巧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邀請艾拉去約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有點事要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你自己把衣服都洗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 這不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧 我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要說的事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃呃… 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次休息日的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的東西還是我自己來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 這是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直以來不都是送去洗衣店的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我突然覺醒了洗衣服技能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是實在無法連內衣也拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}內衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之我自己的東西還是自己洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝你特地幫我洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 忘記約她了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我打算邀艾拉去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等…心急可是吃不了熱豆腐的 司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次你不是打算帶艾拉去遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}結果不是被果斷的拒絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也別在舊傷上撒鹽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}距離感也是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是自以為很親近的去接觸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反而會被討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是您的親身體會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近和女兒搭話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她總是滿臉嫌棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}課長的事還是先丟在一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 你說的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康斯坦斯 把邀人約會的方法傳授給司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的話只要直接真誠地去邀約就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那份感情肯定能傳達給艾拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位也聽聽我的話吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非你幫我整理好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微有點亂我就整理了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真抱歉呢 讓你做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這也是搭檔的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說這週休息日…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 我放在這裡的文件去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那些我還要用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重新再做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}約會的事還是之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 今天就到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比想像中的要順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有重要的事要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也有很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道回去的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用導航就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想稍微表現一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用導航又沒有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒有約她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上的氣勢去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我覺得勉強這麼沒用的司不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 氣勢是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微強硬一點才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在不努力還要等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}時不我待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？！ 還是改天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必須要在今天
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上啊 GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天給司添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 今天艾拉好像和平時不太一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是洗衣服又是收拾桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:06:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要幫得上司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 這週休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果可以的話 我們倆出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什麼樣的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是私下約會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去…去約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不 請和我約會！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去的話就能幫到司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是幫忙的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果你同意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢 說的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是私下約會哦 真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個賭我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天午飯 你請客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}切
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an7\fs22\blur1\c&H8E8688&\bord0\pos(129,36)}主題：多謝昨日關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\an7\fs22\blur1\c&H8E8688&\bord0\pos(123,320)}愛母之家 白井海倫小姐\N\N早安！\N\N非常感謝您昨天抽出時間。\N\N多虧您，讓我學到了很多東西，\N那麼下次也請務必…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 司！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐 輕點輕點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聽說你要去約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不要太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然把艾拉託付給了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可並不代表你工作就能偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像香月姐說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我現在還只是個半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要認真工作才行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去外勤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你中午就吃這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有在好好吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那傢伙最近幹勁滿滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在意的話 你可以幫他做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是很擅長做飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為…為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 現在司腦子裡都是約會的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概也沒法好好評價吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}約會是什麼情況！這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難怪這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哼 居然擔心他 我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}煩死了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後呢 要去哪裡約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個…司說讓我決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 全都推給女方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不負責啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉想去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然這種時候要去電影院啊 水族館啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 繪瑠也能提出這麼保險的建議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克克你當我是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說第一次約會還是保險一點比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿滿的話 會想去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢…可能是海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}海岸還沒開放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以現在人比較少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就可以兩個人悠閒的相處了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牽著一條白色大型犬在海邊散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在浪花中打鬧嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後一邊欣賞慢慢沉入海平面的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一邊互相傾訴愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是 今天不想放你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請永遠不要離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後他們互相…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剛才都是胡說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 記住剛才的話不會有壞處的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿有一顆少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別瞎教多餘的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們的意見不當作參考也行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說回來 你真的沒有想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想去的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 你當天要穿什麼衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就穿這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}私服呢 沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒是有這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是裂了個大口子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就增加花邊修補一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你肯定會擅自加入一些怪趣味 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 我來修補
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滿 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難得的初次約會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必須要好好打扮下才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初次約會…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天去玩的地方 遊樂園怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遊樂園…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能想起的地方只有那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且之前我拒絕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一直覺得那時候傷到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以這回一定要好好和司一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 那就決定了哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,930)\c&H6D5B6E&\an1\fs20\bord0}11月20日 週五 晴\N\N在薇薇的神秘花園看到了好多從沒見過的植物\N而且下次說好要教我很多東西\N好期待啊♪\N要不要買本植物圖鑑呢！！！\N明天休息☆\N\N\N\N還有池塘呢！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,930)\c&H6D5B6E&\an3\fs20\bord0}11月21日 週六 晴\N今天香月又帶我去遊樂園了\N是今年的第三次了\N但是完全沒有厭煩\N香月總是毫無怨言地陪我到最後\N可能香月表面是那副表情 其實很高興
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能想到那個地方…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼感覺今天一大早就這麼熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對 應該是很冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 睡醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這衣服很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從哪裡開始玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\blur2}媽媽 這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你很喜歡這個長椅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日記裡面寫過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前和香月姐搭檔的時候 經常來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在這裡一直坐到太陽下山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看過了很多人的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘記不安之類的所有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心情變得很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐也一直和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她總是在旁邊睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最後一次來是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一次 香月在這裡提出要解除搭檔關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為我給香月添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在這之後就沒來過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不都是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過去高興的事還有悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各種各樣的感情都會湧現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你還喜歡這個遊樂園其他的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雲霄飛車 摩天輪之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道 因為…我沒坐過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一次都沒坐過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那今天要不要都玩一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實這裡還有很多好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不去感受一下的話太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道這樣做是否是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也可能只是我自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要讓艾拉在這每個瞬間都感覺到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我經常從那裡看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼小…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉初次相遇也是在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個時候完全想像不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會有一天像這樣和司一起坐摩天輪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她看起來好像很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}錯…錯誤 這樣我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 醒過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在摩天輪裡突然倒了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣啊 完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是因為你過度疲勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先睡一下 我去拿水過來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我聽說你在約會途中暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可別給艾拉添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就因為這樣我才說外行根本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我給你熬了粥過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趕緊吃了這個睡覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我可不是為了你才去做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你請假了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對我也會有影響的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就照這個樣子去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那傢伙可能已經睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有艾拉在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}萬一覺得我多管閒事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是不爭氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我總是會在關鍵的時候搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}考大學失利也是因為考試當天得了闌尾炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是也是多虧了那場病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才能進來終端服務課
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後和艾拉相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣來看的話 生病似乎也不是什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望司可以一直保持著微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我啊 我的壽命只剩一個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想要一直做你的搭檔直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那樣…可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天玩的開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以後再一起去好嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡了一晚上差不多都好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話不去醫院也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我了個去！ 艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陪了你一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像…要沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}振作點
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
